post.description:
Run get method of smart contract. Stack supports only `num`, `cell` and `slice` types:
```
[
    {
        "type": "num",
        "value": "0x12a"
    },
    {
        "type": "cell",
        "value": "te6..." // base64 encoded boc with cell
    },
    {
        "type": "slice",
        "value": "te6..." // base64 encoded boc with slice
    }
]
```
